    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "just \"be\"? there is no \"being\" without a purpose. i don't know how to exist if i'm not the person i thought i was. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the man staring back. it feels like i'm just occupying space that i don't deserve anymore.",
